  "detailed_description": "<h1>SEASON4 ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/6b68477be346de3d9d4e1bbe36989a2a.avif?t=1773906445\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\"><i>Schedules are subject to change without prior notice.</i></p></p><br><h1>DK ONLINE OFFICIAL SITE</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/208a50cf8f179062869af83cf8bf4346.webp?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/b9f35db94c5b5b1a4ad35f9499544226.webp?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/f02314866c6700054c3709ce28b5e6d6.webp?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/06c4d48b9090f3c2da0315050cc46671.webp?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\"><i>                                                           CHECK THE LINK ON THE RIGHT SIDE</i></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DK Online - Season 4: Annihilation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Opening on <strong>November 25, 2025</strong>, DK Online Season 4 returns stronger than ever, bringing a new era of power, unity, and transformation. Prepare to enter a battlefield where only growth and survival define true heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/3e64a38b5f31df226375ae4e406dd784.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/a9604a428fdc9dc97328304cac97dd17.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/a9604a428fdc9dc97328304cac97dd17.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In DK Online, transformation is the heart of your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over a hundred forms, from noble heroes to ferocious monsters and ancient raid bosses, and grow stronger with every card you claim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each transformation adds to your Transformation Points, while Soul registration awakens deeper potential, allowing you to shape a hero that feels uniquely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/7955f662592f94496a031f3ddbc2d31a.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/f2ba416527753f486b82b46fcae74965.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/f2ba416527753f486b82b46fcae74965.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Season 4, the Guild Stronghold, the Earl's Castle, will be introduced as a new update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seize the Earl’s Castle and make it your guild’s private stronghold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only your members can enter to gather and rest together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside, you’ll find exclusive shops, convenient travel options, and a true home that belongs to your guild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Owning the castle is more than a convenience. It represents pride, power, and your guild’s legacy in the world of DK Online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/1f9e364c1dc7e450c160854f0b391ea5.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/9dafc05c7f93041868c9944132df97fa.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/9dafc05c7f93041868c9944132df97fa.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP in DK Online is more than just combat—it’s a test of true strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > From one-on-one duels to large-scale guild wars and castle sieges, players can rise through the ranks by proving their skill against others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss raids and siege battles all come alive through PvP, creating moments of high-stakes tension and unforgettable victories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Whether you fight for glory, for your guild, or simply to prove you are the strongest, PvP is where legends are forged.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/a99b929f8eefc3c29e7de9e580a0ff58.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/e94a5001a59b93a43b89133aa46d9c9f.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/e94a5001a59b93a43b89133aa46d9c9f.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of DK Online is vast, living, and always expanding. From ancient plains and perilous dungeons to towering fortresses and undiscovered regions, each area offers new challenges and stories. With every season, the realm grows, bringing new maps, new adventures, and new conflicts to conquer. This is a world to explore, shape, and leave your mark on alongside countless other heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A True Classic MMORPG Awaits.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DK Online - Season 4: Annihilation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Opening on <strong>November 25, 2025</strong>, DK Online Season 4 returns stronger than ever, bringing a new era of power, unity, and transformation. Prepare to enter a battlefield where only growth and survival define true heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/3e64a38b5f31df226375ae4e406dd784.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/a9604a428fdc9dc97328304cac97dd17.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/a9604a428fdc9dc97328304cac97dd17.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In DK Online, transformation is the heart of your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over a hundred forms, from noble heroes to ferocious monsters and ancient raid bosses, and grow stronger with every card you claim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each transformation adds to your Transformation Points, while Soul registration awakens deeper potential, allowing you to shape a hero that feels uniquely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/7955f662592f94496a031f3ddbc2d31a.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/f2ba416527753f486b82b46fcae74965.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/f2ba416527753f486b82b46fcae74965.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Season 4, the Guild Stronghold, the Earl's Castle, will be introduced as a new update.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seize the Earl’s Castle and make it your guild’s private stronghold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only your members can enter to gather and rest together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside, you’ll find exclusive shops, convenient travel options, and a true home that belongs to your guild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Owning the castle is more than a convenience. It represents pride, power, and your guild’s legacy in the world of DK Online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/1f9e364c1dc7e450c160854f0b391ea5.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/9dafc05c7f93041868c9944132df97fa.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/9dafc05c7f93041868c9944132df97fa.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP in DK Online is more than just combat—it’s a test of true strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > From one-on-one duels to large-scale guild wars and castle sieges, players can rise through the ranks by proving their skill against others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss raids and siege battles all come alive through PvP, creating moments of high-stakes tension and unforgettable victories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Whether you fight for glory, for your guild, or simply to prove you are the strongest, PvP is where legends are forged.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/a99b929f8eefc3c29e7de9e580a0ff58.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/e94a5001a59b93a43b89133aa46d9c9f.poster.avif?t=1773906445\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781030/extras/e94a5001a59b93a43b89133aa46d9c9f.webm?t=1773906445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of DK Online is vast, living, and always expanding. From ancient plains and perilous dungeons to towering fortresses and undiscovered regions, each area offers new challenges and stories. With every season, the realm grows, bringing new maps, new adventures, and new conflicts to conquer. This is a world to explore, shape, and leave your mark on alongside countless other heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A True Classic MMORPG Awaits.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
